{"tid":1639241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA啟示］煲大里昂雪山獅子旗，等中國人連歐聯都無得睇","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:59:53.000Z","uid":101392,"like":158,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb7ec3638f7b5aa4914863deb74921d2206e230","tid":1639241,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"事緣：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601057/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601057/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jk27M5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjk27M5F.jpg&h=fb3db074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（里昂球迷為左抗議提早開波遷就中國市場，組成雪山獅子旗，FREE TIBET字眼抗議）<br />\n<br />\n火箭GM Morey句「Fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong」呢句咁中性嘅嘢都搞到軒然大波，搞到大陸要抵制NBA<br />\n「雪山獅子旗」直情有分離主義成分<br />\n照計應該仲大鑊<br />\n <br />\n里昂都今日都無道歉聲明 <br />\n唔似Morey咁已經撤回+道歉<br />\n反而NBA要抵制，法甲、歐聯唔使？<br />\n<br />\n一齊喺微博、懂球帝等等中國足球論壇撥火<br />\n叫中共抵制里昂、抵制法甲、抵制歐聯（話如果歐聯唔逐里昂出去，就罷睇歐聯）<br />\n等佢地連法甲、歐聯都無得睇<br />\n<br />\n歐洲佬咁貪錢應該即刻跪<br />\n等歐洲人都感受下，係中共經濟威脅下，佢地都無曬言論自由<br />\nconnect埋歐洲"},{"pid":"988625c6593f9dcc0ece7c9517aa30e125f18340","tid":1639241,"uid":54303,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"全球排華不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78be63ce9d5699a32736e4e0cb4c4b56a92f808","tid":1639241,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc5cf7d53f94549b6256c7fba07b9cb374dabcf9","tid":1639241,"uid":76397,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"988625c6593f9dcc0ece7c9517aa30e125f18340","tid":1639241,"uid":54303,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"全球排華不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"係排共"},{"pid":"66d21da980f5540e535d832395783f738d53d691","tid":16